  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Become an investigator and uncover the hidden truths shrouded in darkness.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3620360/extras/57f6d98a6b1ac3699a01ddbf354dbea5.poster.avif?t=1744675198\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3620360/extras/57f6d98a6b1ac3699a01ddbf354dbea5.webm?t=1744675198\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3620360/extras/57f6d98a6b1ac3699a01ddbf354dbea5.mp4?t=1744675198\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3620360/extras/ae274d4070e0ce8f5b0f2f6252a078a1.poster.avif?t=1744675198\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3620360/extras/ae274d4070e0ce8f5b0f2f6252a078a1.webm?t=1744675198\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3620360/extras/ae274d4070e0ce8f5b0f2f6252a078a1.mp4?t=1744675198\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The protagonist responds to a report of a discovered corpse and heads to the scene. As the investigation progresses, they get closer to uncovering the truth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find passwords and hidden clues, proceed with the investigation, and survive to make it through the game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>With flat 2D graphics and a visual novel-style progression, there are no challenging controls.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3620360/extras/c9f635df4e163d6496ec408b0e63378f.poster.avif?t=1744675198\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3620360/extras/c9f635df4e163d6496ec408b0e63378f.webm?t=1744675198\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3620360/extras/c9f635df4e163d6496ec408b0e63378f.mp4?t=1744675198\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3620360/extras/5b9d1fa4d7e48abcea491bfceff7f529.poster.avif?t=1744675198\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3620360/extras/5b9d1fa4d7e48abcea491bfceff7f529.webm?t=1744675198\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3620360/extras/5b9d1fa4d7e48abcea491bfceff7f529.mp4?t=1744675198\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In The Dark Story: Starving Child, players do not move or jump!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game progresses by clicking on objects on the screen or reading the protagonist's dialogue.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Most actions in the game operate through mouse movement and clicks.</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Look for interactive elements!</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3620360/extras/0c423b3eb6c585be2e3ed6fd407c5f93.poster.avif?t=1744675198\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3620360/extras/0c423b3eb6c585be2e3ed6fd407c5f93.webm?t=1744675198\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3620360/extras/0c423b3eb6c585be2e3ed6fd407c5f93.mp4?t=1744675198\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3620360/extras/fb2d117bb3365efc49dd0d2c69709b77.poster.avif?t=1744675198\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3620360/extras/fb2d117bb3365efc49dd0d2c69709b77.webm?t=1744675198\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3620360/extras/fb2d117bb3365efc49dd0d2c69709b77.mp4?t=1744675198\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game begins by identifying objects that can be interacted with.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Check directly to see what interactions are possible!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Then, gather the necessary information from each element to uncover the truth behind the events!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
